Package: caROC
Type: Package
Title: Continuous biomarker evaluation with adjustment of covariates
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Ziyi Li
Maintainer: Ziyi Li <zli16@mdanderson.org>
Description: Compute covariate-adjusted specificity at controlled sensitivity level, or covariate-adjusted sensitivity at controlled specificity level, or covariate-adjust receiver operating characteristic curve, or covariate-adjusted thresholds at controlled sensitivity/specificity level. All statistics could also be computed for specific sub-populations given their covariate values. 
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: R (>= 3.5), quantreg, RColorBrewer
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr

